• The front of the booth is open (no front wall), the desk is curved and red, stands are in a semi-circle with slight rotations, tables and chairs are placed symmetrically, banners are suspended overhead in three colors, spotlights hang above desk/stands, balloons float inside, and soft pastel cushions lie near seating.
